{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whether we went with the beginning of the evacuation or the end, or the middle, I couldn't say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I know is that it was a snowy winter, and we were being driven day and night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I'm told by my sisters, and I know it for a fact, I fell asleep, completely and totally.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could not manage that march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they just dragged me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just absolutely dragged me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and-- I had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] complete-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had hallucinations that did not measure up to reality.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, I thought I was somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and you see, there was this winter road, covered with snow, and the trees on both sides of the road.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it looked to me like an enclosure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I just thought it was-- whatever it was, I absolutely was cut off from what was happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what was happening was, was just dreadful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the death march was a death march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a march where people were falling by the wayside from exhaustion, from lack of sleep, from hunger, from just not being able to do it anymore and being hit by the-- by a butt of, of the gun, of the rifle, or shot.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Again, and with the dogs, the whole-- it was like, like the same tape, you know, that repeated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Except this is now dead of winter, dark and snowy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And again, we don't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't even remember how many days that lasted, truly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I really slept through that march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They dragged me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we finally one night, I think we were stopped at the barn, or some such big enclosure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were rushing us in and rushing us in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I-- my sisters were pulling me in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I couldn't move fast enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I got hit with a rifle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I fell right at the doorstep to that barn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, I was dead asleep anyhow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But next day, when the commotion started, I was at the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when I woke up, I stood at the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I found my sisters again, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had absolutely no plans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the reason that, first of all, no one experience equaled the other experience.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you could not draw on your experiences.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think that we, the three of us, were all that clever, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are some people are very clever about living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have an onion and exchange it for cigarettes and exchange the cigarettes for whatever, and then they end up with a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never could manage things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I guess, we grew up in another setting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went just being carried, I guess, by the-- by life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were just being-- not that we were passive, but certainly we couldn't be active.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as far as plans are concerned, if there is anything in life you learn from experience, it's how to use your previous experience to your future experience.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in this string of experiences, beginning with the first day of the war, there was absolutely nothing that you could have predicted or foreseen or otherwise applied to plan for anything.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By now we knew that we are slated for destruction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The question was, how long would that take.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How long and how many other things are going to come around to decide our fate?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, right along, I knew that my fate would be decided immediately, if I were to be left alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was no question in mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plans or no plans or experiences, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I were to be alone, I would not survive, I knew it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my passivity was really my complete faith in my two sisters-- their judgment, their love, and, and their protection.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and of course, we supported each other, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were, we were really, in all-- as they say, in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the support that we gave each other-- and we still had these other people around us, you see-- that sustained us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We still were running into these other people, here and there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, that at least, that was a thread from the old life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So maybe you weren't such an absolute reject from life because there was, after all, somebody there who know you, who knew you as that other person in the other life, which was life, and this being not just torture, but some kind of inhuman, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know-- imagination couldn't paint this.",
      "word_count": 56
    }
  ],
